#

Garlic Butter Shrimp with Asparagus and Lemon Zest

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbPaleo

Tags:

SeafoodQuick MealGourmetHealthy

Description

Savory garlic butter shrimp paired with tender asparagus and a refreshing hint of lemon zest, perfect for a quick yet gourmet meal.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Asparagus (trimmed): 1 bunch
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • Lemon (zested and juiced): 1
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Olive oil: 1 tbsp
